- Title (as written in the CV)  \
- Date/year obtained, if present must be written as ISO string. (leave empty if missing)\
Examples:  \
- \'93POS Operations Certificate \'96 H&M Internal Training\'94  \
- \'93Coding Boot Camp, Columbia Engineering\'94  \
- \'93Forklift Operator Certificate\'94\
